1
00:00:00,320 --> 00:00:02,880
Please go out with me!

2
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:08,840
Actually, for a long time now,

3
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:10,760
I've had feelings for you, Kono Mizuki.

4
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:15,400
If you're open to it...

5
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:16,800
I'm sorry.

6
00:00:17,280 --> 00:00:19,120
Thank you for telling me. I'm flattered.

7
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:21,680
But I'm not looking for a relationship right now.

8
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:25,560
I see.

9
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:27,880
That makes sense.

10
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:33,480
I can't! That's hilarious!

11
00:00:35,360 --> 00:00:37,320
Too funny! Your acting was spot on!

12
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:43,040
For a second there, I actually thought it was real.

13
00:00:43,040 --> 00:00:43,600
Huh?

14
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:45,360
You guys were the ones who told me to do it!

15
00:00:46,480 --> 00:00:48,000
Are we done here? Can I go now?

16
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:51,640
Don't tell me you actually believed it?

17
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:53,840
Well, he is a total nerd, after all.

18
00:00:54,040 --> 00:00:55,480
A nerd! Hahaha!

19
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:56,760
That is the perfect way to describe him!

20
00:00:56,760 --> 00:00:57,880
Hey, you guys!

21
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:02,360
Apologize to Kono Mizuki.

22
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:03,920
Iijima Hinata...

23
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:05,640
What? It was just a joke.

24
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:06,520
We were just messing around.

25
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:07,520
I, for one,

26
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:09,680
can't stand pranks like this.

27
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:11,880
Fine, we're sorry.

28
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:18,680
And you.

29
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,520
It's because of those bangs,

30
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,520
that people look down on you.

31
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,880
You're actually not bad-looking.

32
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,640
What?

33
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:30,720
Kono Hazuki...

34
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:31,920
Hmm?

35
00:01:33,150 --> 00:01:34,250
Oh, never mind.

36
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:42,440
They were really mean just now.

37
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,080
Hey, Iijima Hinata?

38
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:45,080
Whoa!
